plan for gpio pins in BCM
theta stepper:     dir  = 22
		   step = 27

z stepper:         dir  = 23
		   step = 24

vl53l1x tof sense: 3v power top left
		   SDA = 2
		   clk = 3
		   shut = 4
		   ground @ pin 9
		   int  = 17

communication pin:
This is to let the other Rpi know 
that the recording line is done.
Once it goes high, that means the 
line is done.
		   outpin = 5
		   inpin  = 6
		   